                      Decorative designs:
                      <locus target="#2r #23r #40r #54v #78v #102v #117v" facs="005 026 043 058 082 106 121">folss. 2r, 23r, 40r, 54v, 78v, 102v, 117v, </locus> (ornate haräg);
